|style="height:40px; text-align:left;"| <font size="4">{{Indent}}'''CYBERNETICS'''</font>
|-
| style="text-align:right;" | <font size="3">''Variable''</font>
|-
|{{Indent}}Treat most cybernetic implants as equivalent advantages: Infravision for a bionic eye, Damage Resistance for dermal armor, etc. Some implants may qualify for the Temporary Disadvantage limitation (p. 115); suitable temporary disadvantages include Electrical (p. 134) and Maintenance (p. 143). These apply to the implant, not to your overall capabilities.

